    {"id":3,"type":"timeseries","title":"Policy decisions","gridPos":{"h":10,"w":24,"x":0,"y":5},"datasource":{"type":"prometheus","uid":"prometheus"},"targets":[{"refId":"A","expr":"sum by (policy_version, policy_disposition) (rate(seocho_governance_policy_decision_count_total[5m]))","legendFormat":"{{policy_version}} {{policy_disposition}}"}]}
